---
// CTA — closing call to action / contact entry point.
// Primary path is the self-connection check-in; the mailto stays as
// a quiet fallback for visitors who'd rather just write.
---

<section id="cta" class="cta">
  <div>
    <div class="eyebrow">05 · Begin</div>
    <h2>
      If something in you is <span class="ital">already turning</span>, we should talk.
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="right">
    <p>
      Begin with a quiet check-in. Ten short questions to show me where you
      are right now. When you finish, you'll receive a short reflection, and
      I'll write back to you personally within a few days.
    </p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/check-in">
      Get Your Free Personalized Assessment
      <span class="btn-arrow" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </a>
    <p style="margin-top: 22px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-faint);">
      Or, if you'd rather just write,
      <a
        href="mailto:anuyu.coach@gmail.com"
        style="color: var(--ink); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);"
        >say hello at anuyu.coach@gmail.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
